## Changing the mediator to a categorical variable to visualize






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# try to set b as a categorical variable 
a<-rnorm(n=100,mean=50,sd=5)
b<-if_else(a<50,0,1)
c<-b+rnorm(n=100,mean=0,sd=1)



mod2.11<-lm(c~a+b)
mod2.11|>
  tbl_regression()
```

